trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventListener.OnEventWritten(System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs)" /> callback.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o retorno de chamada <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventListener.OnEventWritten(System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs)" />.

trans-unit.source: [Supported in the .NET Framework 4.5.1 and later versions]
trans-unit.target: [Suporte somente no .NET Framework 4.5.1 e versões posteriores]

trans-unit.source: Gets the activity ID on the thread that the event was written to.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a ID de atividade no thread no qual o evento foi gravado.

trans-unit.source: The activity ID on the thread that the event was written to.
trans-unit.target: A ID de atividade no thread no qual o evento foi gravado.

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> property accesses thread local storage.
trans-unit.target: Recuperar o valor da <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> propriedade acessa o armazenamento local de thread.

trans-unit.source: This has the following implications:
trans-unit.target: Isso tem as seguintes implicações:

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> field is valid only for the duration of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventListener.OnEventWritten%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> callback.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> campo só é válido durante a <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventListener.OnEventWritten%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> retorno de chamada.

trans-unit.source: If the activity ID is changed during the callback, the activity ID returned by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> property is invalid.
trans-unit.target: Se a ID da atividade é alterada durante o retorno de chamada, a ID de atividade retornado pelo <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> propriedade é inválida.

trans-unit.source: [Supported in the .NET Framework 4.5.1 and later versions]
trans-unit.target: [Suporte somente no .NET Framework 4.5.1 e versões posteriores]

trans-unit.source: Gets the identifier of an activity that is related to the activity represented by the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o identificador de uma atividade que está relacionado à atividade representada pela instância atual.

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the related activity, or <see cref="F:System.Guid.Empty" /> if there is no related activity.
trans-unit.target: O identificador da atividade relacionada, ou <see cref="F:System.Guid.Empty" /> se não houver nenhuma atividade relacionada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.RelatedActivityId%2A> is a child of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.RelatedActivityId%2A> é um filho de <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventWrittenEventArgs.ActivityId%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: An activity ID can be associated with multiple related activity IDs.
trans-unit.target: Uma ID de atividade pode ser associada a várias IDs de atividade relacionada.
